title: The Baby Sitter
description: Hennesey is treating one of Seaman Walkers's children and asked to stay with it until a babysitter arrives.

title: Tell It to the Chaplain
description: When an ailing Chaplain resists the idea of retirement, Hennesey is ordered to examine him.

title: Harvey's Horse
description: After Harvey Spencer Blair becomes a race-horse owner, the Navy hospital takes on a resemblance to a betting syndicate as the aging nap twice gallops to victory at tremendous odds.

title: The Reunion
description: Chick learns that time can do strange things to old friendships when he passes up Captain Shafer's New Year's Eve party to attend a reunion with two service buddies.

title: Harvey Spencer Blair and His Electric Money Machine
Welcome Home, Dr. Blair
description: Dentist Harvey Spencer Blair III signs on for another Navy hitch. He won't be getting his inheritance for a number of years, and even a millionaire has to make a living somehow.
